title: Hawks Edge Lumberjacks, Win LSC Title
text:
Hawks Edge Lumberjacks, Win LSC Title 
By Zach Schneider October 20, 2015 Updated Oct 20, 2015 at 10:46 PM CDT 
Hermantown, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- The Hermantown volleyball team was able to outlast Cloquet on Tuesday night in a 3-1 win, giving the Hawks an outright claim to this year's Lake Superior Conference (LSC) championship. 
Cloquet was up 24-22 in Gam 4 and had an opportunity to force a decisive Game 5, but Hermantown rallied for four straight points to win the game and the match.
